# 🗺️ NeuronFS Project Codemap (2026-04-19)

## 🏗️ Core Architecture
- **cmd/**: Application entry points (CLI, API, Dashboard)
- **internal/**: Core business logic (Domain-Driven)
  - **brain/**: Neuron processing & logic
  - **vfs/**: Virtual File System (jloot)
  - **api/**: REST/WS Handlers
- **mcp/**: Model Context Protocol servers & tools
- **runtime/**: Session-specific data & active states
- **brain_v4/**: Persistent neuron storage (SSOT)

## 🛠️ Key Components
- **pose_converter/**: AI vision data processing
- **dashboard_v4/**: Real-time visualization
- **scripts/**: Automation & Maintenance
